{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"誓以有宮分的窮蒼，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"和所警告的日子，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"以及能証的和所証的日子，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"願掘坑的人們，被棄絕，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"那坑裡有燃料點著的火，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"當時，他們坐在坑邊，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"他們見証自己對信士們的罪行，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他們對於信士們，只責備他們信仰真主——萬能的，可頌的主，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"天地的國權只是他的，真主是見証萬物的。"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"迫害信士和信女而不悔過的人們，必受火獄的刑罰，並受火災的懲治。"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"信道而且行善的人們，必入下臨諸河的樂園，那確是偉大的成功。"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"你的主的懲治，確是嚴厲的。"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"他確能創造，且能再造，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"他是至赦的，是至愛的，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"是寶座的主，是尊嚴的，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"是為所欲為的。"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"你曾聽見軍隊的故事了嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"法老和賽莫德人的故事。"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"不然，不信道的人們陷於否認之中，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"真主是從各方面包羅他們的，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"不然，這是尊嚴的《古蘭經》，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"記錄在一塊受保護的天牌上。"}]}